Player-version-3.2

Changes for this version:

1. Added new methods in chapter model: 
  1) hasMathFormulas - for all domains that has math formulas in them.
  2) needs_formulas_page - for domains that needs formulas page.

2. Added changes for _directions.scss to contain all domains from right
  to left except from the english domain.

3. Added support for the content of the buttons in the DI domain (hasaka). The change
  is written in the item_tx source.

